-- UniCredit Appoints Nicastro General Manager, Fiorentino as Operating Chief
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t   a n d   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 2010-10-26T16:38:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/unicredit-appoints-nicastro-general-manager-fiorentino-as-operating-chief.html
UniCredit SpA  said it named Roberto Nicastro  as general manager and  Paolo Fiorentino  as chief
operating officer.  Sergio Ermotti , a deputy chief executive officer, will
oversee investment banking until a replacement is named, the
bank said in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi at 
 emartinuzzi@bloomberg.net  